blog.description:
The Video Game Art Archive is dedicated to scanning and extracting classic video game artwork at the best resolutions possible!

Support us on Patreon!
We update four times a day with new artwork from long forgotten games that have never had their art available. Looking for a specific game? Check out the Archive! You might get lucky!

summary: speaking of animal crossing, i dont think ive ever mentioned it here but after my dad died, i stayed up for 25 hours straight...
body: speaking of animal crossing, i dont think ive ever mentioned it here but after my dad died, i stayed up for 25 hours straight playing animal crossing on my old ds and when i finally crashed, i woke up feeling more emotionally healthy than i ever thought possible for someone whose dad had just died

Oh and it gets better. My...
body:
Wow, would you look at that! Apparently one of my Kirby fan arts has recently made it to YouTube! 🤯🤩

Oh and it gets better. My cute little Marx happens to be featured in an “Intense Symphonic Kirby Metal” remix video besides! 😍

… how did they know this is my exact favourite genre of music…? 🤔🤯 Go check it out ASAP!

summary: The new zine, UPSTAGED, is live for applications! The focal point of the zine is to get representation for Pokemon that just...
caption:
The new zine, UPSTAGED, is live for applications!

The focal point of the zine is to get representation for Pokemon that just don’t seem to get as much love as they should!

Application link here!

Be sure to apply before March 12th! Acceptance letters will be sent out between today and March 15th.
